  id: 30
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #13 \u2014 Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi cha \u1EDF nh\xE0
    cu\u1ED1i d\xE3y"
  category: 3
  content: "T\xF4i nghe n\xF3i c\xF3 m\u1ED9t ch\xE0ng trai tr\u1EBB \u0111ang t\xECm
    anh trai m\xECnh trong th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1. N\u1EBFu c\u1EADu ta \u0111\u1EBFn
    \u0111\xE2y, cho c\u1EADu ta bi\u1EBFt: anh trai c\u1EADu t\u1EEBng \u1EDF nh\xE0
    s\u1ED1 14, \u0111\xE3 chuy\u1EC3n \u0111i t\u1EEB tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi d\u1ECBch
    b\xF9ng. C\u1EADu \u1EA5y \u0111\u1EC3 l\u1EA1i ch\xECa kh\xF3a v\xE0 m\u1ED9t
    b\u1EE9c th\u01B0 cho ng\u01B0\u1EDDi em. T\xF4i gi\u1EA5u d\u01B0\u1EDBi g\u1EA1ch
    l\xF2 s\u01B0\u1EDFi. Ch\xFAc c\u1EADu \u1EA5y may m\u1EAFn \u2014 khu n\xE0y
    kh\xF4ng c\xF2n an to\xE0n n\u1EEFa."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
